'''''Polyhedron'' 83''' was a roleplaying magazine from [[May]] of [[1993]]. It contained many roleplaying articles, including a rules supplement for the [[West End Games]] ''[[Star Wars]]'' [[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game|D6]] system. The article was called ''[[Milk Run]]'' and was written by [[Sterling Hershey]].

